		<description><![CDATA[Print PDF Zach awakes to ferocious gusting. With luck Lev won&#8217;t have heard his groan. Their world has been compressed into this small, temporary shelter where they may be warm, they may be fed, they may even be safe, but Zach knows that if he were to risk a few steps beyond the tent, he&#8217;d [...]]]></description>
