			<itunes:subtitle>Print  PDF  - Stella had been the only person allowed to trim Zach&#039;s hair till Laura offered to take over the task. This once, however, Stella insisted on plunking him down on a kitchen chair in her back room and draping a towel round his shoulders.</itunes:subtitle>
